@page "/"

<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<h1>Hello, world!</h1>

<p>Welcome to your Blazor app with authentication.</p>

<div class="alert alert-info mt-4">
    <h5>Architecture Info</h5>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>NavMenu:</strong> InteractiveWebAssembly - works without constant server connection</li>
        <li><strong>Auth Pages:</strong> Static SSR with cookie auth</li>
        <li><strong>Other Pages:</strong> InteractiveAuto - Server first, then WASM</li>
        <li><strong>Auth State:</strong> Cookie (server) + PersistentComponentState (WASM)</li>
    </ul>
</div>
